00:32:50.000 --> 00:32:51.000
He did not charge them.

00:32:51.000 --> 00:32:52.000
He did not charge them.

00:32:52.000 --> 00:32:53.000
Okay.

00:32:54.000 --> 00:33:02.000
He didn't worry about the charges for those that had gotten beaten up and bruised up.

00:33:02.000 --> 00:33:04.000
That was his giving to the movement.

00:33:04.000 --> 00:33:05.000
That's right.

00:33:05.000 --> 00:33:07.000
That was his contribution.

